OL,6,FA man who touched an 8-year-old girl's
OL,7,Fbottom inside a Tesco in Portsmouth
OL,8,Fand then assaulted a police officer
OL,9,Fhas been jailed.
OL,11,FSurajit Ghosh sexually assaulted the
OL,12,Fchild on Saturday 27 May 2023 inside
OL,13,Fthe supermarket on Crasswell Street,
OL,14,Fbefore running off.
OL,16,FGhosh was then chased through the
OL,17,Fsupermarket by a family member of the
OL,18,Fgirl, before the man ran out of the
OL,19,Fstore.
