OL,6,FOfficers reviewed CCTV and then
OL,7,Ftracked Ghsosh down to his home on
OL,8,FDrummond Road, where he was found
OL,9,Fhiding behind a sofa.
OL,11,FHe became aggressive and threatened to
OL,12,Fstab officers whilst resisting arrest.
OL,13,FHe also dug his fingernails into a
OL,14,Fpolice officer's hand, drawing blood.
